title: Ep 122: Last Week's Top Buys!: A Mirror, The Lazy Susan Organizer, Fake Plants

description:
Welcome to another episode of Top Buys, a weekly Gee Thanks! ep highlighting the top 3 purchases podcast listeners and the Gee Thanks! community at large bought the week before. 


Without further ado, here are the top 3 buys from the week of Mar 21, 2022!


  • The Target Valenti Kate and Laurel Mirror: https://rstyle.me/+vBUrMw4SDFhxjWHe-GGXrA 
  • The Rotating Lazy Susan Organizer: https://rstyle.me/+6IgSUy6dMVyV6I7-jgjejw 
  • Big Fake Plants: https://rstyle.me/+FGYPSUDonTDPP20lvOhdbw

 

Things tangentially mentioned:


  • The Anthropologie Mirror Everyone Has: https://rstyle.me/+iXFXrqgO8yRTbAb_RsSVEQ 
  • Clear Boxes for Shoes: https://rstyle.me/+OaZ7mRUBTa6ZQ5ECByZ-WQ 
  • Fake Snake Plants: https://amzn.to/3wRr4Zo 
  • Fiddle Leaf Fern Care: https://stumpplants.com/journal/fiddle-leaf-fig-guide 
  • Planter Baskets for FAKE Plants: https://rstyle.me/+Pl1OoAxpdkHNeo3tmz48Fw 

 

Shop our Amazon Storefront: https://www.amazon.com/shop/geethanksjustboughtit 


Gee Thanks! appreciates its supporters, especially Alley Peplinski, Becca Sheaffer, Allie Nagy, Angi James and Erin Gibson! 


Want to support? Join the Patreon! Sign up: https://www.patreon.com/geethanksandfriends** 


Join the Facebook group: https://www.facebook.com/groups/geethanks 


Follow along with recs (and share your own via DM) on the “Gee Thanks, Just Bought It!” Instagram: www.instagram.com/geethanksjustboughtitpod and shop all of our recs here: www.geethanksjustboughtit.com
